	<span>OPENING OF NEW END STAGE RENAL DISEASE FACILITY IN JACKSONVILLE, ALABAMA</span>
<p>	Effective July 22, 2008 Physician Choice Dialysis received Medicare Certification for the opening of its new dialysis center located in Jacksonville, Alabama.  The Medical Director is Dr. B.S. Bheemanathini.  We are proud of the great work the PCD team has displayed in connection with the opening of this facility in such a short period of time.  The address of the facility is: 331 Henry Road Southwest, Jacksonville, Alabama.
</p>
<p>	 Physicians Choice Dialysis is a nurse driven physician owned organization with a mission to provide the highest quality care to its patient population.  The company owns, manages, develops and operates end stage renal disease programs throughout the country. 
